Please next time do not use a pacman frog or any type of frog. Frogs actually have cutaneous respiration, meaning they breathe through their skin a bit. This means that any chemicals and natural oils on your skin can easily affect a frog and make it very ill. Same with newts and salamanders. Putting that animal in that type of risk is not ok you might not have known so I'm trying not to give you too hard of a time just don't handle them in the future. Thanks!
